WEBVTT

00:00:06.509 --> 00:00:09.509
Okay kids, it's time to practice our Bible books.

00:00:09.509 --> 00:00:12.509
Are you ready to try the rest of the Hebrew Scriptures?

00:00:12.509 --> 00:00:14.509
Ready, Jeremiah!

00:00:14.509 --> 00:00:18.510
In spite of opposition, he's still preached.

00:00:18.510 --> 00:00:19.510
Lamentations!

00:00:19.510 --> 00:00:22.510
The sadness that God's people suffered then.

00:00:22.510 --> 00:00:28.019
Ezekiel! A watchman who gave warnings faithfully.

00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:29.019
Daniel!

00:00:29.019 --> 00:00:33.020
Jehovah saved him from the lion's den.

00:00:33.020 --> 00:00:34.020
Hosea!

00:00:34.020 --> 00:00:38.020
How loyal love surpasses sacrifice.

00:00:38.020 --> 00:00:39.020
Joel!

00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:43.020
Salvation when God's judgment day begins.

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:44.020
Amos!

00:00:44.020 --> 00:00:47.020
We need to hate the bad and love the good.

00:00:47.020 --> 00:00:49.020
Obadiah!

00:00:49.020 --> 00:00:52.020
The Edomites would perish for their sins.

00:00:52.020 --> 00:00:53.020
Jonah!

00:00:53.020 --> 00:00:57.020
God used a fish to turn this man around.

00:00:57.020 --> 00:00:58.020
Micah!

00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:02.020
Jehovah simply asked that we do good.

00:01:02.020 --> 00:01:03.020
Naham!

00:01:03.020 --> 00:01:07.019
God's prophecy that Nineveh must fall.

00:01:07.019 --> 00:01:08.019
Habakkuk!

00:01:08.019 --> 00:01:12.019
Jehovah's Day will come right when it should.

00:01:12.019 --> 00:01:13.019
Zephaniah!

00:01:13.019 --> 00:01:18.519
The great day of Jehovah God is near.

00:01:18.519 --> 00:01:21.519
Haggai! The precious ones to God are gathered in.

00:01:21.519 --> 00:01:22.519
Zechariah!

00:01:22.519 --> 00:01:26.519
His prophecies fulfilled in Jesus Christ.

00:01:26.519 --> 00:01:27.519
Malachi!

00:01:27.519 --> 00:01:31.519
He told how Jesus preaching would begin.
